Android Studio
- auto import header: goto affected line, alt+enter

- UI
	- Get view from an xml layout
TextView guessTextView = (TextView) findViewById(R.id.guessTextView);

- Data
	- Get string from the strings.xml
String string = getString(R.string.hello);
where the strings.xml contains
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<resources>
    <string name="hello">Hello!</string>
</resources>

- Java Iteration styles: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/18410035/ways-to-iterate-over-a-list-in-java

- Adding 'assets' (e.g. csvs)
--- drop into '/src/main/assets' (ASSETS_FOLDER_RELATIVE_PATH in .iml)